如果你想要在两台不同的电脑上传输东西的话，而且你有没有任何外挂硬盘/闪盘等， 你该怎么办？<br />
很简单！靠Windows 自带的共享功能！<br />
<blockquote class="bq_warning">
在一切进行之前<br />
请确定你的两台/多台电脑都在同一个网络上<br />
<blockquote class="bq_info">
注：该网络不一定需要连接外网的功能（就是不一定需要internet access）</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<br />
<blockquote class="bq_info">
笔者运行环境：<br />
Windows 7 Ultimate x86</blockquote>
<h1>
【设置Sharing Option】</h1>
1、打开Control Panel<br />
2、点击Network and Internet<br />
<blockquote class="bq_info">
注：如果你看到不一样的显示方式的话<br />
请将上方的View By转换成Category<br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-OqsXtgoeRmU/UyzmdNOx6sI/AAAAAAAAG34/floO1JmrmUE/s1600-h/image%25255B5%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-pNnaNSTGiaE/UyzmgENUlkI/AAAAAAAAG4A/v4Q7_GihP9g/image_thumb%25255B1%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="232" style="background-image: none; border-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="786" /></a></blockquote>
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-RMWIwIf4XFA/UyzmhiQmzII/AAAAAAAAG4I/rkmiRzmyASg/s1600-h/image%25255B2%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-5JS6K2VXSXg/UyzmjMMt8LI/AAAAAAAAG4M/BSLjJ2HAYwc/image_thumb.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a><br />
<br />
3、点击 Network and Sharing Center<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-zl87Ed-tB6M/UyzmkRKx-xI/AAAAAAAAG4Y/ZjjKTpC95CE/s1600-h/image%25255B8%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-Gr-Hc1zKFFY/UyzmlduW77I/AAAAAAAAG4g/ALl-VgPnmRc/image_thumb%25255B2%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="210" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="603" /></a><br />
<br />
4、点击Choose homegroup and sharing option<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-Nxdv1tsuVbs/Uyzmmav7jmI/AAAAAAAAG4o/o4KNwht8PqI/s1600-h/image%25255B11%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-CWUZ3QdmC0c/Uyzmnrz7pfI/AAAAAAAAG4w/KG5FyedHphg/image_thumb%25255B3%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="375" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="616" /></a><br />
<br />
5、点击 Change advanced sharing settings…<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-Ntvl6eTgqC0/UyzmoZUD5jI/AAAAAAAAG44/JnBTR6qinys/s1600-h/image%25255B14%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-5sriDjgDWGQ/Uyzmp5LFHJI/AAAAAAAAG5A/YcP1w-gI2xw/image_thumb%25255B4%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="404" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="548" /></a><br />
<br />
6、选择Home or Work<br />
<blockquote class="bq_warning">
注：也可能是Public<br />
依情况而定<br />
笔者连接的WiFi 设置成了Home Network<br />
所以选择Home</blockquote>
确保 Public folder sharing 已经开启<br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-JwF2Qr6_rKY/Uyzmqk3XG_I/AAAAAAAAG5I/ASPTXKf96rQ/s1600-h/image%25255B17%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-yFPHkVz6Syk/UyzmrnKA8sI/AAAAAAAAG5Q/MFsmKhMX4Gs/image_thumb%25255B5%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="534" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="584" /></a><br />
<br />
7、你也可以开启密码设置<br />
<blockquote>
如果你开启了密码<br />
那么连接时<br />
就会有个对话框<br />
需要你输入user 和 password<br />
这里的user 就是你电脑login 的username<br />
password 也是一样</blockquote>
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-pL4T33SZqgI/UyzoUcpfbDI/AAAAAAAAG5k/S5LJtXW9JpU/s1600-h/image%25255B20%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-ntIptdHMYrM/UyzoZYEbUzI/AAAAAAAAG5s/NwSnB54o0pM/image_thumb%25255B6%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="485" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="578" /></a><br />
<br />
8、就可以点击Save Changes 了<br />
<br />
<h1>
【开始Share 文件夹】</h1>
这里就以共享一个文件夹为例子：<br />
1、在任何一个文件夹上，右击选择Properties<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-Elr0wjN6ac8/Uyzoi03r3QI/AAAAAAAAG50/Yl23GJwDnFs/s1600-h/image%25255B23%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-l6spZGuDV0s/Uyzomteo7II/AAAAAAAAG58/xoWCs1cv9EE/image_thumb%25255B7%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a><br />
2、点击Sharing， 点击Share…<br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-kIbnjr40XDA/UyzorkDjKPI/AAAAAAAAG6E/LvFYwiaxPJA/s1600-h/image%25255B29%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-q4fbi7o6wX8/Uyzo2_uG3VI/AAAAAAAAG6M/wWqKK3pbxWI/image_thumb%25255B9%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a><br />
3、在下拉菜单中选择homegroup<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-pQgR2KNwdaA/UyzpG9RDSVI/AAAAAAAAG6U/vhEBmQWEsec/s1600-h/image%25255B32%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-XoXfMnWAY7E/UyzpL4k-spI/AAAAAAAAG6c/zREsUnla8iE/image_thumb%25255B10%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="451" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="622" /></a><br />
<br />
4、点击Add<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-vu0vA9g58AI/UyzpVESyLjI/AAAAAAAAG6k/Q9HIZR5L1vs/s1600-h/image%25255B35%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-J2-9tZp0gBk/Uyzpe9BJ2gI/AAAAAAAAG6s/TWIYoC7Wzto/image_thumb%25255B11%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="451" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="622" /></a><br />
<br />
5、在Permission Level 中选择 Read / Write <br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-nWDZ466k5KI/Uyzpl4k4HQI/AAAAAAAAG60/xzIF7m_HcJc/s1600-h/image%25255B38%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-CULOYdr_tr0/Uyzpv0zyjcI/AAAAAAAAG68/V35PnC2ceG8/image_thumb%25255B12%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="451" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="620" /></a><br />
<br />
6、点击Share<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-XECjIzHYUzE/UyzwDi5aYCI/AAAAAAAAG7U/QTj3gDSo31A/s1600-h/image%25255B41%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-kVJjYrc2qdM/UyzwHzIerPI/AAAAAAAAG7c/abJl5Xa1uwA/image_thumb%25255B13%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="451" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="622" /></a><br />
<br />
7、然后就完成了！<br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-Dn90RWUfJKs/UyzwKpmXitI/AAAAAAAAG7k/_BKHY09niWE/s1600-h/image%25255B44%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-ePQxma1pUOA/UyzwORpifzI/AAAAAAAAG7s/8kTsTcIRI1E/image_thumb%25255B14%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="480" style="background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="371" /></a><br />
<br />
8、然后打开Start Menu<br />
输入CMD<br />
按Enter<br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-JFbyTl4TrZY/UyzwRPtHLNI/AAAAAAAAG70/c1M0G-aVH8M/s1600-h/image%25255B50%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-z6b5IM9imzQ/UyzwVHv34fI/AAAAAAAAG78/0C3mfma2x9E/image_thumb%25255B16%25255D.png?imgmax=800" height="410" style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" width="389" /></a><br />
<br />
9、输入ipconfig<br />
按下Enter<br />
找到你连接的网络<br />
这里是Wireless Network Connection<br />
然后记下IPv4 Address<br />
<a href="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-Nh9npuEB9Gw/UyzwbpfPicI/AAAAAAAAG8E/ZZ8rScZ_yTQ/s1600-h/image%25255B59%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-tzS9IXuCtxc/UyzwiX4It_I/AAAAAAAAG8M/QcHTBpVqRvI/image_thumb%25255B19%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a><br />
<br />
<h1>
【连接共享的文件夹】</h1>
<blockquote class="bq_info">
测试环境：Windows XP</blockquote>
1、打开My Computer<br />
2、输入刚刚记下的IP地址<br />
按下Enter<br />
<a href="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-9DXbFgQ3IDs/Uyzwnk3iCoI/AAAAAAAAG8U/lojNeXmHDAU/s1600-h/image%25255B62%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/-dxxuvSD6nmo/Uyzwq3l2rnI/AAAAAAAAG8c/ACKEq8PE07A/image_thumb%25255B20%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a><br />
<br />
3、如果你之前有开启密码的话，你就会看到这个对话框<br />
输入用户名和密码就可以了<br />
点击OK<br />
<a href="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-bcknJ0bgYEI/Uyzwvl7kqyI/AAAAAAAAG8k/66S8JDLnVeI/s1600-h/image%25255B65%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/-LBI1elzsoLE/Uyzw0fmHsJI/AAAAAAAAG8s/GOPz2F31Kjo/image_thumb%25255B21%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a><br />
<br />
4、完成！<br />
<a href="http://lh4.ggpht.com/-zrudGktiM1U/Uyzw-WSSqBI/AAAAAAAAG80/NCG4-3YXnuo/s1600-h/image%25255B68%25255D.png"><img alt="image" border="0" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/-m3NVPWau01o/UyzxjNgWJ5I/AAAAAAAAG88/lGxooir_Fj8/image_thumb%25255B22%25255D.png?imgmax=800" style="background-image: none; border: 0px; display: inline; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px;" title="image" /></a>